lead_paragraph: Left-arm spinner Rangana Herath claimed five wickets as Sri Lanka took control of the second and final test against Zimbabwe on day three on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Herath Puts Zimbabwe in a Spin as Sri Lanka Extend Lead
